{"tid":1267764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"祝大家ご武运を！ ごぶうんを！","createTime":"2019-06-30T05:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T05:33:41.000Z","uid":193234,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e23561470c385c456deecaab1e30ddc669dcf68b","tid":1267764,"uid":193234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"義士的本領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                                  改:步兵的本領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬朵白花作為衣襟的花色<br />\n其景如花在獅子山上被風吹散<br />\n當花開與香港男兒一同奮起<br />\n<br />\n幾吋長的水撥算不上武器<br />\n幾尺長的長傘又能做甚麼?<br />\n要知道這裏有整整一百年<br />\n千錘百鍊的香港魂<br />\n<br />\n守護吾旗的義士們<br />\n常備的總數有二百萬<br />\n在十八餘處駐軍<br />\n並夢想着有一天能卸甲歸田<br />\n<br />\n如果有仇視我們的狗<br />\n就從九龍送出運兵船<br />\n姑且讓海之人護送我們一次<br />\n<br />\n讓所有人知道能在敵陣立足<br />\n軍隊的主力在我們這裏<br />\n最後的決勝是我們的使命"},{"pid":"f5e4c929cf33ab6c1293d4940e04622985bb611d","tid":1267764,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yn7ASQz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYn7ASQz.jpg&h=551baa69&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}